data.description: Home Sweet Home! This cozy 4 bedroom home is in a highly desirable McAllen location on Ware Road & Gumwood, close to South Texas College, HEB, McAllen Convention Center and shopping. Less than 8 minutes walking distance to STC and just a 5 minute drive to Highway 83. This cozy home is really in the HEART of McAllen. This 4 bedroom and 2 bath home is a perfect starter home or investment property if considering Air BnB or long term leases. The roof is brand new as it was installed less than a year ago. There is also a bonus room detached from main home! Schedule your showing and make an offer!
